	directAnswerHtml={`<strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">If you're in high school, the Father's Heart Bible™ is for you.</strong> You carry more than people see — the pressure to perform, the comparison that never turns off, the quiet question of whether you're actually enough. The <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Father's Heart Bible™</a> is a fresh English translation you can read and <em>listen to</em> free on your phone — and it reveals God as a <em>Father</em> from beginning to end. Whether you searched "Bible verses for high schoolers," "verses for anxiety," or "does God love me" — the answer starts in one place: your worth was never your GPA, your follower count, or anyone's opinion. You are His beloved, right now, before you achieve a single thing.`}
