		{ ref: `Galatians 1:10`, slug: `galatians`, ch: 1, text: `Am I now seeking the approval of people, or of my Father? If I were still trying to please people, I would not be a servant of the One who loves me.`, note: `You can stop performing for everyone's approval — His is the only one that finally sets you free.` },
